quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  52,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  52,1,qasam hai tor ki
  52,2,aur aik aisi khuli kitaab ki
  52,3,jo raqeeq jald mein likhi hui hai
  52,4,aur abad ghar ki
  52,5,aur onche chhat ki
  52,6,aur mojzan samandar ki
  52,7,ke tairay rab ka azaab zaroor waqay honay wala hai
  52,8,jisay koi dafaa karne wala nahi
  52,9,woh uss roz waqay hoga jab aasman buri terhan dagmagay ga
  52,10,aur pahar uray uray phiren ge
  52,11,tabahi hai uss roz unn jhutlanay walon ke liye
  52,12,jo aaj khail ke tor par apni Hujjat bazyon mein lagey hue hain
  52,13,jis din inhen dhakkay maar maar kar naar jahannum ki taraf le chala jaye ga
  52,14,"uss waqt unn se kaha jaye ga ke"" yeh wohi aag hai jisay tum jhtlaya karte thay"
  52,15,ab batao yeh jaadoo hai ya tumhe soojh nahi raha hai ?
  52,16,"jao ab jhulso iss ke andar, tum khuwa sabr karo ya nah karo, tumahray liye yaksaa hai, tumhe waisa hi badla diya ja raha hai jaisay tum amal kar rahay thay"
  52,17,mut-taqi log wahan baghoon aur nematon mein hon ge
  52,18,"lutaf le rahay hon ge unn cheezon se jo unn ka rab inhen day ga, aur unn ka rab unhen dozakh ke azaab se bacha le ga"
  52,19,( un se kaha jaye ga ) khao aur piyo mazay se apne unn aamaal ke siilay mein jo tum karte rahay ho
  52,20,woh aamnay samnay bichay hue takhton par takiye lagaye baithy hon ge aur hum khobsorat aankhon wali hooren unn se bayah den ge
  52,21,jo log imaan laaye hain aur unn ki aulaad bhi kisi darja imaan mein un ke naqsh qadam par chali hai un ki uss aulaad ko bhi hum ( jannat mein ) unn ke sath mila den ge aur unn ke amal mein koi ghata un ko nah den ge har shakhs apne ksb ke aiwz rehan hai
  52,22,"hum unn ko har terhan ke phal aur gosht, jis cheez ko bhi un ka jee chahay ga, khoob diye chalay jayen ge"
  52,23,wahan woh aik dosray se jaam sharaab lapak lapak kar le rahay hon ge jis mein nah yawa goi hogi nah bad kirdari
  52,24,aur unn ki khidmat mein woh larke dorrtay phir rahay hon ge jo unhi ke liye makhsoos hon ge aisay khobsorat jaisay chhupa kar rakhay hue moti
  52,25,yeh log aapas mein aik dosray se ( duniya mein guzray hue ) halaat poucheen ge
  52,26,yeh kahin ge ke hum pehlay apne ghar walon mein drtay hue zindagi busr karte thay
  52,27,aakhir-kaar Allah ne hum par fazl farmaya aur hamein jhalsa dainay wali howa ke azaab se bacha liya
  52,28,"hum pichli zindagi mein usi se duayen mangte thay, woh waqai bara hi mohsin aur Raheem hai"
  52,29,"pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum nasiyaat kiye jao, apne rab ke fazl se nah tum کاہن ho aur nah Majnoon"
  52,30,kya yeh log kehte hain ke yeh shakhs shayar hai jis ke haq mein hum gardish ayyaam ka intzaar kar rahay hain ?
  52,31,"inn se kaho acha intzaar karo, mein bhi tumahray sath intzaar karta hon"
  52,32,kya inn ki aqlain iِnhain aisi hi baatein karne ke liye kehti hain? ya Dur haqeeqat yeh inaad mein hadd se guzray hue log hain ?
  52,33,kya yeh kehte hain ke iss shakhs ne yeh quran khud ghurr liya hai? asal baat yeh hai ke yeh imaan nahi lana chahtay
  52,34,agar yeh apne iss qoul mein sachey hain to aِsi shaan ka aik kalaam bana layein
  52,35,kya yeh kisi khaaliq ke baghair khud peda ho gay hain? ya yeh khud apne khaaliq hain ?
  52,36,ya zameen aur asmano ko unhon ne peda kya hai? asal baat yeh hai ke yeh yaqeen nahi rakhtay
  52,37,kya tairay rab ke khazanay inn ke qabzay mein hain? ya unn par aِnhi ka hukum chalta hai ?
  52,38,kya inn ke paas koi seerhi hai jis par charh kar yeh aalam baala ki sun gun letay hain? inn mein se jis ne sun gun li ho woh laaye koi khuli Daleel
  52,39,kya Allah ke liye to hain betiyan aur tum logon ke liye hain betay ?
  52,40,kya tum inn se koi ajar mangte ho ke yeh zabardasti pari hui chti ke boojh taley dabey jatay hain ?
  52,41,kya inn ke paas ghaib ke haqayiq ka ilm hai ke uss ki bana par yeh likh rahay hon ?
  52,42,kya yeh koi chaal chalna chahtay hain? ( agar yeh baat hai ) to kufar karne walon par un ki chaal ulti hi parre gi
  52,43,kya Allah ke siwa yeh koi aur mabood rakhtay hain? Allah pak hai uss shirk se jo yeh log kar rahay hain
  52,44,yeh log aasman ke tukre bhi girtay hue dekh len to kahin ge yeh baadal hain jo amde chalay aa rahay hain
  52,45,"pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, aِnhin inn ke haal par chore do yahan taq ke yeh apne uss din ko poanch jayen jis mein yeh maar giraye jayen ge"
  52,46,jis din nah inn ki apni koi chaal inn ke kisi kaam aeye gi nah koi inn ki madad ko aeye ga
  52,47,"aur uss waqt ke anay se pehlay bhi zaalmon ke liye aik azaab hai, magar inn mein se aksar jantay nahi hain"
  52,48,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, apne rab ka faisla anay taq sabr karo, tum hamari nigah mein ho tum jab utho to apne rab ki hamd ke sath is ki tasbeeh karo"
  52,49,raat ko bhi is ki tasbeeh kya karo aur setaaray jab palatne hain uss waqt bhi
